{"id":182,"parent_id":179,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":182,"title":"Ephesians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Eph.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","The Gentiles are fellow heirs with Israel—The love of Christ surpasses all understanding."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.1","order":"03.12.003.20107"},["b","1"],"For this cause I Paul, the prisoner of Jesus Christ for you Gentiles,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.2","order":"03.12.003.20108"},["b","2"],"If ye have heard of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"dispensation"],"of the grace of God which is given me to you-ward:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.3","order":"03.12.003.20109"},["b","3"],"How that by revelation he made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"known"],"unto me the mystery; (as I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"wrote"],"afore in few words,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.4","order":"03.12.003.20110"},["b","4"],"Whereby, when ye read, ye may understand my knowledge in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"mystery"],"of Christ)"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.5","order":"03.12.003.20111"},["b","5"],"Which in other ages was not made known unto the sons of men, as it is now",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"revealed"],"unto his holy apostles and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"prophets"],"by the Spirit;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.6","order":"03.12.003.20112"},["b","6"],"That the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Gentiles"],"should be fellowheirs, and of the same body, and partakers of his promise in Christ by the gospel:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.7","order":"03.12.003.20113"},["b","7"],"Whereof I was made a minister, according to the gift of the grace of God given unto me by the effectual working of his power."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.8","order":"03.12.003.20114"},["b","8"],"Unto me, who am less than the least of all saints, is this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"grace"],"given, that I should preach among the Gentiles the unsearchable",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"riches"],"of Christ;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.9","order":"03.12.003.20115"},["b","9"],"And to make all",["i","men"],"see what",["i","is"],"the fellowship of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"mystery"],", which from the beginning of the world hath been hid in God, who",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"created"],"all things by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"Jesus Christ"],":"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.10","order":"03.12.003.20116"},["b","10"],"To the intent that now unto the principalities and powers in heavenly",["i","places"],"might be known by the church the manifold wisdom of God,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.11","order":"03.12.003.20117"},["b","11"],"According to the eternal",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"purpose"],"which he purposed in Christ Jesus our Lord:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.12","order":"03.12.003.20118"},["b","12"],"In whom we have boldness and access with confidence by the faith of him."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.13","order":"03.12.003.20119"},["b","13"],"Wherefore I desire that ye faint not at my tribulations for you, which is your glory."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.14","order":"03.12.003.20120"},["b","14"],"For this cause I bow my knees unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Father"],"of our Lord Jesus Christ,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.15","order":"03.12.003.20121"},["b","15"],"Of whom the whole",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"family"],"in heaven and earth is named,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.16","order":"03.12.003.20122"},["b","16"],"That he would grant you, according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"riches"],"of his glory, to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"strengthened"],"with might by his Spirit in the inner man;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.17","order":"03.12.003.20123"},["b","17"],"That Christ may dwell in your hearts by faith; that ye, being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"rooted"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"grounded"],"in love,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.18","order":"03.12.003.20124"},["b","18"],"May be able to comprehend with all saints what",["i","is"],"the breadth, and length, and depth, and height;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.19","order":"03.12.003.20125"},["b","19"],"And to know the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"love"],"of Christ, which passeth knowledge, that ye might be filled with all the fulness of God."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.20","order":"03.12.003.20126"},["b","20"],"Now unto him that is able to do exceeding abundantly above all that we ask or think, according to the power that worketh in us,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.21","order":"03.12.003.20127"},["b","21"],"Unto him",["i","be"],"glory in the church by Christ Jesus throughout all ages,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"world"],"without end. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.2a","order":"03.12.003.20128"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.3a","order":"03.12.003.20130"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.27.26-27"},"Col. 1:27 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.3b","order":"03.12.003.20132"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-lost"},"TG Scriptures, Lost"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.4a","order":"03.12.003.20134"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.25"},"Rom. 16:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/1.9.9-11"},"Eph. 1:9 (9–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.5a","order":"03.12.003.20136"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.5b","order":"03.12.003.20138"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.6a","order":"03.12.003.20140"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gentiles"},"TG Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.8a","order":"03.12.003.20142"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.8b","order":"03.12.003.20144"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.9a","order":"03.12.003.20146"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"TG Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.9b","order":"03.12.003.20148"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/creation"},"TG Creation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-creator"},"God, Creator"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.9c","order":"03.12.003.20150"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.11a","order":"03.12.003.20152"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-purpose-of"},"TG Earth, Purpose of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.14a","order":"03.12.003.20154"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godhead"},"TG Godhead"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.15a","order":"03.12.003.20156"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family"},"TG Family"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.16a","order":"03.12.003.20158"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.16b","order":"03.12.003.20160"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.11"},"Col. 1:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.17a","order":"03.12.003.20162"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.7"},"Col. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.17b","order":"03.12.003.20164"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.23"},"Col. 1:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.19a","order":"03.12.003.20166"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.21a","order":"03.12.003.20168"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.112"},"D&C 76:112"],"."]]}
